OL,3,C#54m jump in costs behind pensions
OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FThe costs behind a system to help
OL,7,Fpeople to see all their pensions
OL,8,Ftogether online have jumped by #54
OL,9,Fmillion, with no date yet set for when
OL,10,Fit will be made available to the
OL,11,Fpublic, a spending watchdog has said.
OL,13,FDelays to the pensions dashboards
OL,14,Fprogramme have partly been due to a
OL,15,Flack of digital skills and ineffective
OL,16,Fgovernance, the National Audit Office
OL,17,F(NAO) said.
OL,19,FThe estimated cost of the programme
OL,20,Fhas jumped by 23%, from #235 million
OL,21,Fin 2020 to #289 million in 2023.
