OL,3,C#54m jump in costs behind pensions
OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FThe report said a "range of factors"
OL,7,Fhas led to the estimated cost of the
OL,8,Fprogramme increasing by #54 million.
OL,10,F"These include an increase in supplier
OL,11,Fcosts, changes to the Money and
OL,12,FPensions Service's (MaPS) underlying
OL,13,Fcosting assumptions, and the period
OL,14,Fcovered being extended by two years to
OL,15,F2031-32," the report said.
OL,17,FThe previous #235 million estimate had
OL,18,Fcovered 10 years from 2019-20 to 2029-
OL,19,F30, including five years of live
OL,20,Frunning.
