OL,3,C#54m jump in costs behind pensions
OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FThe report said that from April 2019
OL,7,Fto March 2024, MaPS spent #59 million
OL,8,Fon the pensions dashboards programme.
OL,10,FSince 2019-20, the programme has been
OL,11,Ffunded mainly through two industry
OL,12,Flevies that also fund MaPS' other
OL,13,Foperations, it said.
OL,15,FThey are the financial services
OL,16,Findustry levy, which is levied on
OL,17,Fregulated financial institutions such
OL,18,Fas banks and building societies, and
OL,19,Fthe general pensions levy, which is
OL,20,Flevied on occupational pension schemes.
