OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FAn estimated 16.3 million people could
OL,7,Fstand to benefit from pensions
OL,8,Fdashboards, enabling them to view
OL,9,Finformation about their private,
OL,10,Fworkplace and state pensions all
OL,11,Ftogether.
OL,13,FBut the NAO's report said: "DWP has
OL,14,Fnot yet specified when pensions
OL,15,Fdashboards will become available to
OL,16,Fthe public but, due to the later
OL,17,Fconnection deadline, this is expected
OL,18,Fto be later than previously expected."
