OL,3,C#54m jump in costs behind pensions
OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FHaving an overview of multiple pension
OL,7,Fpots could help people to plan their
OL,8,Fretirement, make up shortfalls and
OL,9,Ffind "lost" retirement savings. An
OL,10,Festimated #26.6 billion-worth of
OL,11,Fpension pots are lost.
OL,13,FPension providers and schemes are
OL,14,Frequired to connect to government
OL,15,Fdigital architecture that supports
OL,16,Fdashboards by October 31 2026 ` a year
OL,17,Flater than previously planned.
