OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FThere were previously 23 separate
OL,7,Fstaging deadlines for connecting up,
OL,8,Fdepending on pension schemes' size and
OL,9,Ftype. The first deadline was August 31
OL,10,F2023 and the last deadline had been
OL,11,Fset at October 31 2025.
OL,13,FThe DWP delegated responsibility for
OL,14,Fdelivering the programme to the MaPS,
OL,15,Fan "arm's-length" body, in 2019.
OL,17,FBut it did not have assurance at the
OL,18,Foutset that MaPS had the capacity and
OL,19,Fcapability to deliver a major digital
OL,20,Fprogramme such as this, the NAO said.
