OL,4,Cdashboards programme
OL,6,FA DWP review last year found that
OL,7,Fmultiple factors had contributed to
OL,8,Fthe delivery problems, including a
OL,9,Flack of skilled digital resources and
OL,10,Fineffective programme governance.
OL,11,FThese factors had also been raised in
OL,12,Fearlier reviews of the programme
OL,13,Fcarried out by the Infrastructure and
OL,14,FProjects Authority, the NAO said.
OL,16,FThe programme is being reset and DWP
OL,17,Fand MaPS have made progress in some
OL,18,Fareas, the NAO said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/17
