OL,6,FThe DWP and MaPS have started to make
OL,7,Fchanges in response to lessons
OL,8,Flearned, revising programme governance
OL,9,Farrangements and strengthening how DWP
OL,10,Fworks with its arm's-length bodies,
OL,11,Fthe report said.
OL,13,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,14,F"Delivery delays due to shortfalls in
OL,15,Fdigital capacity and capability have
OL,16,Fpushed back the final deadline for
OL,17,Fpension providers and schemes to
OL,18,Fconnect to the PDP (pensions
OL,19,Fdashboards programme) by a year, with
OL,20,Fno date currently set for citizens to
OL,21,Fbenefit.
