OL,6,F"Though progress has been made during
OL,7,Fthe reset, DWP and MaPS must continue
OL,8,Fto work closely to ensure the final
OL,9,Fstages of the PDP are delivered
OL,10,Fsmoothly and the public can begin to
OL,11,Fhave access to this important service."
OL,13,FDame Meg Hillier, chairwoman of the
OL,14,FPAC said: "Clear and simple pensions
OL,15,Fdashboards would help people properly
OL,16,Funderstand their pensions ` preventing
OL,17,Fthem from missing out on entitlements
OL,18,Fhidden in 'lost pots' and helping them
OL,19,Fplan for their future.
